snippet.title: Suikoden I & II HD Remaster Gate Rune and Dunan Unification Wars - Trailer | TGS 2024
snippet.description:
Check out the new trailer for the Suikoden HD remaster collection, which brings these classic RPGs up to date with enhanced art, UI, and battle systems. The collection will be avaialble on modern consoles from March 2025.
